1. Danas *crvenim* u licu zbog sunca. (Today I'm blushing because of the sun.)
2. U mom ormaru su samo *crvene* majice. (There are only red shirts in my closet.)
3. *Crvena* jabuka je moj omiljeni voćni sok. (Red apple is my favorite fruit juice.)
4. Zbog loše cirkulacije, moje ruke su *crvene*. (Due to poor circulation, my hands are red.)
5. Na semaforu se upalila *crvena* boja. (The red light turned on at the traffic light.)
6. Dres *crvene* zvezde je rasprodat. (Red Star's jersey is sold out.)
7. *Crveni* tepih na dodeli nagrada je bio spektakularan. (The red carpet at the awards ceremony was spectacular.)
8. Voće bogato *crvenim* pigmentom je jako zdravo. (Fruit rich in red pigment is very healthy.)
9. Sutra moram *ocrveneti* kosu, jer izrastak je prevelik. (Tomorrow I have to dye my hair red because the regrowth is too big.)
10. U horor filmu, krv je *crvene* boje. (In a horror movie, blood is red.)

(Note: In Serbian, the word "crvene" can be used as a verb, adjective, and noun, and the form of the word changes depending on the context.)